My lord, Madam was found
by Lord Chong Yang.

125
00:10:06,420 --> 00:10:08,220
Will he give you any trouble?

126
00:10:12,180 --> 00:10:13,860
He can't even protect himself.

127
00:10:14,740 --> 00:10:15,980
He won't have time for me.

128
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:18,060
By the way,

129
00:10:19,220 --> 00:10:20,980
anything going on at Ye Mansion?

130
