133
00:10:29,260 --> 00:10:31,180
Seems like Zhu Yingying
hasn't made a move.

134
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:33,300
If we count the days,

135
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:35,940
the gu I planted on Ji Nanxing,

136
00:10:36,660 --> 00:10:37,900
