139
00:11:13,280 --> 00:11:16,760
♪I cling to the past like a wanderer♪

140
00:11:16,920 --> 00:11:20,360
♪Still guarding the gate to old memories♪

141
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:26,200
♪Eternal promise♪

142
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:34,400
♪How do I heal after losing you?♪

143
00:11:35,040 --> 00:11:41,320
♪How could I let go of all this pain?♪

144
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:47,160
♪The more I hold back,
the closer you feel♪

145
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:50,560
♪The more it hurts,
the more I break♪

146
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:56,120
♪Every snowflake feels like your kiss♪

147
00:11:56,400 --> 00:12:03,160
♪Let time pause,
let fireflies fill the sky♪

148
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:10,360
♪In your arms,
I lose focus—tears fall♪

149
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:15,560
♪And everything else just fades away♪

150
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:19,000
♪You belong only to me♪

151
